    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与最多 4 名同伴组成的团队一起，清除感染程序生成的中世纪村庄的瘟疫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062930/extras/6e9dc113bc164cbfc39f1761a1338f7f.poster.avif?t=1728568434\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062930/extras/6e9dc113bc164cbfc39f1761a1338f7f.webm?t=1728568434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062930/extras/6e9dc113bc164cbfc39f1761a1338f7f.mp4?t=1728568434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瘟疫已经在这片土地上定居下来，居住在其中的村民和生物已经变异成超乎想象的恐怖生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062930/extras/b92c25b0523a15cff2594919dba8f4e1.poster.avif?t=1728568434\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062930/extras/b92c25b0523a15cff2594919dba8f4e1.webm?t=1728568434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062930/extras/b92c25b0523a15cff2594919dba8f4e1.mp4?t=1728568434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在村庄间穿梭的过程中，发现并收集各种原料，找到正确的组合来制作解药。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062930/extras/b45b98e0ca6ab6c9338ce6a346a2cf21.poster.avif?t=1728568434\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062930/extras/b45b98e0ca6ab6c9338ce6a346a2cf21.webm?t=1728568434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062930/extras/b45b98e0ca6ab6c9338ce6a346a2cf21.mp4?t=1728568434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 最多 4 人在线合作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 近距离语音聊天</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 程序生成的村庄和区域</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 恐怖有趣的怪物和人工智能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 瘟疫驴子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062930/extras/4e9fb4dbea6b2db8835cda185e8e81b7.poster.avif?t=1728568434\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062930/extras/4e9fb4dbea6b2db8835cda185e8e81b7.webm?t=1728568434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062930/extras/4e9fb4dbea6b2db8835cda185e8e81b7.mp4?t=1728568434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
